# Unicode.GeneralCategory.openPunctuation

**Case**

An opening punctuation mark of a pair.

## Declaration

```swift
case openPunctuation
```

## Discussion

This value corresponds to the category `Open_Punctuation` (abbreviated `Ps`) in the [https://unicode.org/reports/tr44/#General_Category_Values].
